&lt;p&gt;North Point Technology is looking to hire a Cloud Infrastructure Architect to design and automate cloud infrastructure across AWS GovCloud and ADC (C2S/SC2S) isolated regions. The qualified candidate must have an active TS/SCI security clearance and will build Infrastructure as Code, CI/CD pipelines, and secure networking within air-gapped, classified enclaves. The ideal candidate combines deep AWS and DevOps expertise with hands-on experience automating hardening and compliance in a DoD/IC environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position centers on designing and implementing Infrastructure as Code using CloudFormation or Terraform within ADC and GovCloud isolated regions. The architect will build CI/CD pipelines in air-gapped environments with approval gates and change management, and design the underlying network architecture - multi-account landing zones, Transit Gateway networking, and hybrid connectivity via Direct Connect and VPN - within classified enclaves. Additional work includes automating patching, AMI hardening, drift detection, and STIG/CIS compliance enforcement, and implementing observability and logging strategies that meet audit and records retention requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills/Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Infrastructure as Code using CloudFormation or Terraform within ADC/GovCloud isolated regions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;CI/CD pipeline architecture in air-gapped environments with approval gates and change management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Multi-account landing zones, Transit Gateway networking, and hybrid connectivity (Direct Connect, VPN) in classified enclaves&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Automation of patching, AMI hardening, drift detection, and STIG/CIS compliance enforcement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Observability and logging strategies compliant with audit and records retention requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active Top Secret/SCI security clearance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;North Point Technology is &lt;strong&gt;THE BEST &lt;/strong&gt;place to work for curious-minded engineers motivated to support our country’s most crucial missions!&amp;nbsp; We focus on long term projects, leveraging the latest technology in support of innovative solutions to solve our customer’s most difficult problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At North Point Technology, EMPLOYEES come first!&amp;nbsp; We value our employees by providing excellent compensation, benefits, and a flexible work-life balance. We strive for a close-knit and open atmosphere where the owners are always directly available to our team members.&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
