&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MES Controls Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;North Point Technology is seeking an experienced MES Controls Engineer to support manufacturing operations in a high-volume discrete manufacturing environment. This role focuses on Manufacturing Execution Systems (MES), PLC integration, real-time production execution, and automation system reliability. The ideal candidate will work closely with engineering, operations, and production teams to support and optimize MES-driven manufacturing processes.&lt;/p&gt;
